  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "add the crab meat and smoked salmon, cook for 2-3 minutes until heated through.",
    "add the hollandaise sauce and stir to combine.",
    "season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "add the cooked penne rigate pasta to the skillet and toss to combine.",
    "transfer the pasta to a bento box and garnish with chopped parsley and dill."
